#   - **wit-bindgen** (WIT bindings
#     generator for Rust + C + Java +
#     Python)
#   - **jco** (JavaScript / TypeScript
#     bindings; THIS AXIS Node closer)
#   - **StarlingMonkey** (the WASM-
#     packaged SpiderMonkey for jco
#     componentize)
#   - **cargo-component** (cargo
#     extension for WASM Component
#     workflows)
#
# Multi-axis canonical-Node author/org
# cohort extension (now spanning 28
# distinct individuals/orgs after R1558):
#   - + Guy Bedford + Victor Adossi +
#     Bytecode Alliance (@bytecodealliance/
#     jco; THIS AXIS; canonical Node
#     WebAssembly Component Model
#     tooling)
#
# Guy Bedford's broader Node ecosystem
# footprint:
#   - **jco** (canonical Node WASM
#     Component Model tooling; THIS
#     AXIS)
#   - **es-module-shims** (the canonical
#     polyfill for ECMAScript module
#     features in browsers; widely
#     deployed on the web)
#   - **systemjs** (the SystemJS module
